@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC / Backoffice Operator" as Actor
participant ":System" as System

== Get Route Details by ID ==

activate Actor
Actor -> System : getRouteById(routeId)
activate System

note right of System: The system finds the route\nby its ID and returns its details\nincluding current version data.

System --> Actor : informs operation success and returns route details
deactivate System

== List All Routes from/to a Specific Airport ==

Actor -> System : listRoutesByAirport(iataCode)
activate System

note right of System: The system returns all active routes\nwhere the airport is either\nthe origin or the destination.

System --> Actor : informs operation success and returns list of routes
deactivate System
deactivate Actor
@enduml